      "excerpt": "Building this changed how I start new features. I now try to write down what I am making, why that direction was chosen, where the work is, and what should happen next before asking an assistant to continue. I do not se…",
      "content": "Closing Thoughts\nBuilding this changed how I start new features. I now try to write down what I am making, why that direction was chosen, where the work is, and what should happen next before asking an assistant to continue. I do not see lee spec kit as a grand methodology. It is a small workbench for reducing repeated explanation when working with AI. A strong model helps, but without records and order it still loses the thread quickly. lee spec kit is the tool I made to reduce that problem in my own workflow.",
